                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Unless otherwise required by law, we retain your information for as long as it takes to achieve the goals mentioned in this privacy notice. Data will be used only for reports and analytics after it has served its purpose.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        6. SECURITY MEASURES
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        APO employs reasonable technical, organizational, and administrative measures to safeguard personal data against unauthorized access, loss, or alteration. However, APO cannot guarantee the absolute security of data transmission or storage.
                    </p>

                    <p>
