                        APO shall not be held liable for any misuse or unauthorized access to information by third parties, provided that reasonable security measures are in place to protect the data. APO endeavors to ensure the confidentiality and integrity of personal information but cannot guarantee absolute security against all potential risks.
                    </p>

                    <p>
